Slurm
```json
{
"application": "Slurm",
"details": [
"The script is designed to run on a Slurm workload manager.",
"It requests a single node for the job.",
"It specifies the output log file path.",
"The job name is set to 'script_list.txt'.",
"The script uses a job array with 337 tasks.",
"The runtime for each task is limited to 1 hour.",
"The script uses GNU Parallel for parallel execution of tasks.",
"The script sets the chunk size for parallel execution to 1.",
"The script uses 1 core for parallel execution.",
"The script sets the number of threads per command to 1."
],
"resourceRequirements": [
"GNU parallel",
"R version 4.0.3",
"Miniconda3 version 4.9.2",
"Sed",
"Bash"
]
}
```
